*Standard Operating Procedure*<br><br><br>
*Purpose: Providing Remote/Offsite Support:*<br><br>
# Providing Remote/Offsite Support:
As outlined in our SLA, blueSteele with offer remote support under the following ways. <br>

#### Scope of Services

- Monitored Email Support
- Telephone support during monitored hours
- Planned or Emergency Onsite assistance
- Remote assistance
- Monthly system health check <br>

#### Service Delivery Times <br>
-Telephone support: 9:00 A.M. to 5:00 P.M. Monday-Friday
-Email support: 9:00 A.M. to 5:00 P.M. Monday-Friday <br>

#### Service Requests <br>

Remote assistance will be provided based on the priority of the issue.
-0-4 hours (during business hours) for issues classified as Urgent priority.
-0-8 hours (during business hours) for issues classified as High priority.
-Within 48 hours for issues classified as Medium priority.
-Within 5 working days for issues classified as Low priority

*For more information, contact the Blue Steele Helpdesk by phone or email.* <br><br> 
*-Dean Weiss*